query: COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, datname, pid, usesysid, usename, application_name, client_addr, client_port, backend_start, xact_start, query_start, waiting, query , state, state_change FROM pg_stat_activity) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV, HEADER);

COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, datname, pid, usesysid, usename, application_name, client_addr, client_port, backend_start, xact_start, query_start, waiting, query , state, state_change FROM pg_stat_activity) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV);

COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, a.schemaname, a.relname, seq_scan, seq_tup_read, idx_scan, idx_tup_fetch, n_tup_ins, n_tup_upd, n_tup_del, n_tup_hot_upd, n_live_tup, n_dead_tup, heap_blks_read, heap_blks_hit, idx_blks_read, idx_blks_hit, toast_blks_read, toast_blks_hit, tidx_blks_read, tidx_blks_hit FROM pg_statio_all_tables a, pg_stat_all_tables b WHERE a.relid = b.relid) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV);
